{"kind":"article","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Run scripts automatically when a VM boots."}],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/SpooktacularKit\/documentation\/SpooktacularKit\/Provisioning"},"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"major":0,"minor":3},"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"content","content":[{"type":"heading","anchor":"Overview","level":2,"text":"Overview"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"macOS virtual machines don’t have a cloud-init equivalent. Spooktacular","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"provides provisioning modes to bridge this gap. Today, SSH provisioning","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"is fully working. Disk-inject is in progress, and two more modes (guest","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"agent and shared-folder watcher) are planned.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"heading","anchor":"Choosing-a-Mode","level":3,"text":"Choosing a Mode"},{"type":"table","header":"row","rows":[[[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Mode"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Status"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Works without setup?"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Network needed?"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Best for"}],"type":"paragraph"}]],[[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/SpooktacularKit\/documentation\/SpooktacularKit\/ProvisioningMode\/ssh","isActive":true}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Working","type":"text"}],"type":"strong"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Need SSH enabled"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Yes"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Cloned VMs with SSH"}],"type":"paragraph"}]],[[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/SpooktacularKit\/documentation\/SpooktacularKit\/ProvisioningMode\/diskInject","isActive":true}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"In progress","type":"text"}],"type":"strong"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Yes"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"No"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Fresh IPSW installs, CI runners"}],"type":"paragraph"}]],[[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/SpooktacularKit\/documentation\/SpooktacularKit\/ProvisioningMode\/agent","isActive":true}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Planned"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Need agent installed"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"No"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"OCI images (future)"}],"type":"paragraph"}]],[[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/SpooktacularKit\/documentation\/SpooktacularKit\/ProvisioningMode\/sharedFolder","isActive":true}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Planned"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Need watcher"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"No"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"No-disk-modify environments"}],"type":"paragraph"}]]]},{"type":"heading","anchor":"SSH-Working","level":3,"text":"SSH (Working)"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"After boot, Spooktacular discovers the VM’s IP, connects via SSH,","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"and executes your script. You get real-time output streaming.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"bash","code":["spook start my-vm \\","    --user-data ~\/setup.sh \\","    --provision ssh \\","    --ssh-user admin"]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Requires:"}],"type":"strong"},{"text":" Remote Login enabled in the guest","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"(System Settings -> General -> Sharing -> Remote Login).","type":"text"}]},{"type":"heading","anchor":"Disk-Inject-In-Progress","level":3,"text":"Disk Inject (In Progress)"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Before the VM boots, Spooktacular mounts the guest’s data volume","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"and writes a standard macOS LaunchDaemon that executes your script.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"This is the only mode that will work on a completely vanilla macOS","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"install. This mode is currently being implemented.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"bash","code":["spook create my-vm --from-ipsw latest \\","    --user-data ~\/setup.sh \\","    --provision disk-inject"]},{"type":"heading","anchor":"Guest-Agent-Planned","level":3,"text":"Guest Agent (Planned)"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The Spooktacular guest agent will communicate over VirtIO socket — a","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"direct host-guest channel that works without networking. This mode","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"is planned for a future release.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"heading","anchor":"Shared-Folder-Planned","level":3,"text":"Shared Folder (Planned)"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The script will be delivered via a VirtIO shared folder. A watcher","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"daemon in the guest will execute new scripts automatically. This","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"mode is planned for a future release.","type":"text"}]}]}],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/spooktacularkit\/provisioning"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"metadata":{"role":"collectionGroup","title":"Provisioning Virtual Machines","roleHeading":"API Collection","modules"